metadata.Plot: After a near death incident leaves Kristin scarred with a terrifying connection to the Spirit World, she uses any means necessary to block it. But when she and her fiance move into a new home, Kristin quickly realizes they are not alone. Clues of its horrific past are revealing themselves and the Dark Force that dwells in the house is not going to stop until it gets what it wants.
